informationEmbed.title: Welcome to The Goose House!
informationEmbed.body:
The Goose House began as a community of esports industry professionals looking to network and game together. Since then, it has expanded, allowing passionate gamers and esports fans to come together and connect.

**We are the #1 European VALORANT Community, supported directly by RIOT.**

4.title: Honks and Weekly Skirmish (3/3)
4.body:
ü¶Ü **Honks**
Honks are our currency, like raffle tickets ‚Äì the more you have, the more likely you will win our monthly giveaway. You can earn honks by taking part in and winning events like our Weekly Skirmish.

‚öîÔ∏è **Weekly Skirmish**
We run a weekly skirmish every week of the year. The tournaments are split into Iron to Plat and Diamond to Radiant groups. We also have anti-smurf detection to ensure you are playing with people of a similar skill level.

You can learn more about the Weekly Skirmish in <#1055443176707588177>.

ruleEmbed.body:
**You must be at least 16 years old:**
This is an age-restricted server to ensure the safety of everyone in our community.

**You must be respectful: **
You should respect all members regardless of ethnicity, gender, sexual orientation, or beliefs. Harassment and hate speech will not be tolerated. Political topics should also be avoided.

**You must keep profiles appropriate: **
Your username, nickname, avatar, and custom status must be appropriate. This includes zalgo, blank usernames, slurs, or other offensive material.

**You must ask before messaging a server member: **
Please do not contact server members unsolicited. This includes Twitch Partners and Industry members. Do not ping staff unless you have a reason.

**You must respect the TOS of other platforms: **
You should respect the rules of Discord and game publishers and continue to abide by them here. For example, no discussion of account sharing or boosting.
